{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":98,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他們在他們的主那裡的報酬是下臨諸河的常住的樂園，他們將永居其中，真主喜悅他們，他們也喜悅他；這是畏懼真主者所有的。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"當大地猛烈地震動"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"拋其重擔"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"說\"大地怎麼啦"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日, 大地將報告它的消息。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"因為你的主已啟示了它"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"在那日, 人們將紛紛地離散"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"以便他們得見自己行為的報應。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"行一個小螞蟻重的善事者, 將見其善報; 作一個小螞蟻重的惡事者, 將見其惡報。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以喘息而奔馳的馬隊盟誓"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以蹄發火花的馬隊盟誓"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以早晨出擊"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"捲起塵埃"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"攻入敵圍的馬隊盟誓"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人對于主, 確是孤負的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他自己對那孤負確是見証的"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他對于財產確是酷好的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"難道他不知道嗎？當墳中的朽骨被揭發"}]}